### Test 1: Get stats for user (after logging sessions)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stats?userId=1
Accept: application/json

### Test 2: Get stats for user with no sessions (should return empty stats)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stats?userId=2
Accept: application/json

### Test 3: Missing userId (should fail with 400)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stats
Accept: application/json
